{"tid":1180804,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"劉兆佳：修訂逃犯條例上升至國家主權問題","createTime":"2019-06-01T06:18:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-01T06:32:43.000Z","uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"6efa9dd893d412fc58498f30335034f978205d14","tid":1180804,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T06:18:48.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】全國港澳研究會副會長劉兆佳表示，修訂逃犯條例涉及維護國家安全，與廿三條立法同樣重要，認為政府不會因為民意壓力而撤回修例。<br />\n<br />\n劉兆佳：「不排除西方國家會在香港製造事端，破壞一國兩制，令香港成為危害國家安全的基地。所以整體情況如此不同下，今次逃犯條例修訂已上升至國家主權、國家安全、國家聲譽、特區管治能力以至廿三條以後立法的問題。」"},{"pid":"df6949bef23afc481f415eb092de236b023fbcba","tid":1180804,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T06:18:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=350120\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D350120&d=RSiYdbgXC1SHA4i8VFLgbWWzMblEAwKPRhfqpO9yGDY%3D&h=1b567b8e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D350120&h=805c66b9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=350120</a>"},{"pid":"0e8997bf496589f46be7e9c76884e11c7d19e570","tid":1180804,"uid":31637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T06:20:23.000Z","msg":"早修早著, 遲修訓唔著"},{"pid":"0c976bfc99c288570c77a43b8333f68cbf4620d2","tid":1180804,"uid":40250,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T06:22:51.000Z","msg":"劉兆佳講得岩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3956fd2bf337bbe3dc3523f115a174c1b8258f7e","tid":1180804,"uid":12510,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T06:23:58.000Z","msg":"無錯，所以要當廿三條咁反<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35f5eed8c96853f16311ba239b51066cdcd57c45","tid":1180804,"uid":156203,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T06:28:4